Qty.
Many pieces of okra (vendaikkai).

Instructions.
1. Pour a lot of oil to cover the bottom of the pan. Add cumin seeds.

2. Add okra. Once everything is fried, then add 1 spoon chili
powder, 1-1/2 spoons coriander powder, 1/5-2/5 spoon of turmeric,
and add salt accordingly. Add kitchen king masala at the end.

3. Optionally, add a little tomato pur√©e to make a gravy. Or, optionally
add one or two spoons of yogurt.

